INSERT INTO `org_groups` VALUES (10,1,'2013-02-07 21:44:49','2013-02-28 01:14:30','The department or support systems responsible for personnel sourcing and hiring, applicant tracking, skills development and tracking, benefits administration and compliance with associated <br>government regulations<br><br>HR responsibilities include:<br>payroll<blockquote><ul><li>benefits,&nbsp;</li><li>hiring &amp;&nbsp;firing</li><li>keeping up to date with state and federal tax laws.<br></li></ul></blockquote>','http://www.entrepreneur.com/encyclopedia/term/82184.html',NULL,NULL,'HR','Human Resources',NULL),(18,1,'2013-02-27 17:32:10','2013-02-27 19:05:21','<ol><li><p>The Group Accounting Team reports via the Group Accountant and Deputy Finance Director (Financial Reporting) to the Finance Director and Director of Finance &amp; Financial Strategy.</p><p>Please click on the thumbnail below to see the organisation chart for the Group Accounting Team.</p><p><a href=\"http://www2.warwick.ac.uk/services/finance/aboutthefo/fosections/gat/group_accounts_team_mayl_2012.gif\"><img alt=\"GAT Org Chart\" src=\"http://www2.warwick.ac.uk/services/finance/aboutthefo/fosections/gat/group_accounts_team_mayl_2012.gif?maxWidth=200&amp;maxHeight=200\" title=\"Image: http://www2.warwick.ac.uk/services/finance/aboutthefo/fosections/gat/group_accounts_team_mayl_2012.gif?maxWidth=200&amp;maxHeight=200\"></a></p></li></ol>','http://www2.warwick.ac.uk/services/finance/aboutthefo/fosections/gat/','2013-02-27 08:00:00','2013-02-28 08:00:00','ACCOUNTING','Accounting',NULL),(19,1,'2013-02-27 17:42:56','2013-02-27 19:22:34','<div><br></div><div>Our <b>Junior Sales Associates</b> are the core function of our business. Junior Sales Associates identify, initiate, and&nbsp;</div><div>nurture relationships, both over the phone and via e-mail, with decision makers and qualify sales opportunities for&nbsp;</div><div>our Sales Associates. Our Junior Sales Associates generate sales-ready leads with the help of a great sales support team.<br><br><ol></ol><ol><li>Manage a high volume of outbound calls to warm marketing lists to uncover qualified sales opportunities<br></li><li></li><li>Collect and record the contact information of prospects and leads</li><li>&nbsp;Navigate corporate structures to identify decision makers and determine buying process</li><li>Identify prospect\'s business needs and goals to determine solution</li><li>Work closely with Sales Manager to increase close ratio and number of customers</li></ol></div>','www.jrsalesteam.com','2013-02-27 08:00:00','2013-02-28 08:00:00','JR SALE STEAM','Jr. Sales Team',NULL),(20,1,'2013-02-27 17:45:54','2013-02-27 21:19:53','<div><ul><li><li>Sales Order Processing,&nbsp;</li><li>Production and Shipping</li><li>Post Sales Support, etc</li></li><li>Assist in facilities master planning.&nbsp;<br></li><li>Maintain and report space utilization inventory.&nbsp;<br></li><li>Prepare and submit deferred maintenance plan, and hazardous substance removal plans and requests.&nbsp;<br></li><li>Supervise repair and maintenance work on college facilities and equipment.&nbsp;<br></li><li>Oversee maintenance and operation staff; participate in the selection of personnel; evaluate maintenance&nbsp;<br></li><li>and operations supervisor, review evaluations of maintenance workers, groundskeepers, custodians and&nbsp;<br></li><li>warehouse staff; provide technical guidance and direction; assist in transfer, promotion, and salary&nbsp;<br></li><li>decisions; identify training needs; recommend policy, procedures and personnel changes.&nbsp;<br></li></ul></div>','www.maintenanceoperations.com','2013-02-27 08:00:00','2013-02-28 08:00:00','OPERATIONS','Maintenance/Operations',NULL),(21,1,'2013-02-27 17:49:31','2013-02-27 19:08:12','<div>The Marketing Team is responsible for brand awareness, public&nbsp;</div><div>representation, and prospecting for new members.&nbsp;</div><div>Responsibilities:&nbsp;</div><div>1. Review current marketing pieces (ads, displays, brochures, and folders) and&nbsp;</div><div>bring fresh, current ideas.&nbsp;</div><div>2. Develop and periodically review the schedule for events, ads, and articles to increase awareness.</div><div>3. Personally contact three to five organizations in the defined target markets as assigned by staff. Report to staff the results of contacts so that appropriate follow-up can take place.&nbsp;</div><div>4. Be willing to represent ALDE at non-ALDE events, hosting roundtables, breakfasts, etc. The team leader and ALDE staff will review the budget, target markets, and member availability to determine event coverage. <br>5. Develop an e-strategy. Review the website quarterly. Facilitate bet</div>','www.marketingteam.com','2013-02-27 08:00:00','2013-02-28 08:00:00','MARKETING','Marketing Team',NULL),(22,1,'2013-02-27 17:51:49','2013-02-27 19:48:53','Implementing Product Development<br>Product development professionals design and create new products or improve existing products for an organization. These professionals often work as part of the product&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ehow.com/facts_6739944_job-description-product-development.html#\"><span>marketing<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://images.intellitxt.com/ast/adTypes/icon1.png\"></span></a>&nbsp;team and often work in the manufacturing industry.<span><br><br></span>','www.productdevelpment.com','2013-02-27 08:00:00','2013-02-28 08:00:00','PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT','Product Development',NULL),(23,1,'2013-02-27 17:54:33','2013-02-27 20:52:16','Reviewing current systems<br><ul><li>Presenting ideas for system improvements, including cost proposals</li><li>Working closely with analysts, designers and staff</li><li>Producing detailed specifications and writing the programme codes</li><li>Testing the product in controlled, real situations before going live</li><li>Preparation of training manuals for users</li><li>Maintaining the systems once they are up and running</li></ul>','www.informationtechnology.com','2013-02-27 08:00:00'