INSERT INTO `projects` VALUES (2,1,'2013-02-27 17:57:40','2013-02-27 22:29:16','<a href=\"http://projects.eclipse.org/datatools/\" title=\"Link: http://projects.eclipse.org/datatools/\">The Moon Data Tools Platform</a>- provides extensible frameworks and exemplary tools, enabling a diverse set of plug-in offerings specific to particular data-centric technologies and supported by the DTP ecosystem.<br>','http://projects.eclipse.org/projects/datatools','2013-02-27 08:00:00','2013-02-28 08:00:00','MOON DATA TOOLS PLATFORM','Eclipse Data Tools Platform',NULL),(3,1,'2013-02-27 18:08:12','2013-03-01 21:04:44','Creating and expanding so that we can further territory.<br><br><b>Marketing plan</b><span>&nbsp;may be part of an overall&nbsp;</span><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Business_plan\" title=\"Link: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Business_plan\">business plan</a>.</b><span>&nbsp;Solid&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marketing_strategy\">marketing strategy</a><span>&nbsp;is the foundation of a well-written marketing plan. While a marketing plan contains a list of actions, a marketing plan without a sound strategic foundation is of little use.</span><br>','www.artsmarket.com','2013-02-27 08:00:00','2013-03-29 07:00:00','ARTSMARKET','ArtsMarket',NULL),(4,1,'2013-02-27 18:09:25','2013-03-01 22:55:56','TOOL INTEGRATION PROJECT\'S&nbsp;objective is to create a browser-based open tool integration platform which is entirely focused on developing for the web, in the web. Tools are written in JavaScript and run in the browser. Great care has been taken to provide a web experience for development, rather than to recreate the traditional desktop IDE experience in a browser tab.<br><br>The Orion project\'s focus is creating components, services, and libraries for building web-based development tools. This includes browser client infrastructure built using widely adopted web technologies such as HTML, JavaScript, and CSS. Also included is server-side infrastructure needed by such development tools. This includes infrastructure supporting file management, search, user management, preferences, generic source control, compare, file history, editors, and user interface widgets and controls required to build development tools. Also of importance are the necessary tools to be able to self-host, i.e. to develop Orion using Orion itself. We believe this feedback loop of being our own customer is critical to us producing stable, high quality, and truly useful development tools. As such, tools for specific web technologies used by Orion will be in scope for this project. This includes development tools for programming JavaScript, HTML5, CSS, web site production and related technologies. Orion will also produce source control integration tools as required for our development purposes. Producing these exemplary tools will allow us to continuously evaluate the quality and value of our framework components and libraries.<br>','http://projects.eclipse.org/projects/eclipse.orion','2013-02-27 08:00:00','2013-02-28 08:00:00','TOOL INTEGRATION PROJECT','Tool Integration Project',NULL),(5,1,'2013-02-27 18:10:25','2013-02-27 22:29:45','<a href=\"http://www.eclipse.org/eclipse/\" title=\"Link: http://www.eclipse.org/eclipse/\">The MoonTop-Level Project</a><span>&nbsp;- an <b>open source</b>, robust, full-featured, commercial-quality, industry platform for the development of highly integrated tools and&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.eclipse.org/rcp/\" title=\"Link: http://www.eclipse.org/rcp/\">rich client applications</a>.<br>','http://projects.eclipse.org/projects/eclipse','2013-02-27 08:00:00','2013-02-28 08:00:00','MOON','MOON Project',NULL),(6,1,'2013-02-27 18:14:17','2013-02-27 19:02:17','<span>BIRT is an open source Eclipse-based reporting system that integrates with your Java/Java EE application to produce compelling reports.<br><blockquote><ul><li><span>This project addresses both the design time needs of report creation as well as the run-time requirements of report generation and deployment. The project adopts and supports accepted open standards wherever feasible.</span><br></li></ul></blockquote></span>','http://projects.eclipse.org/projects/birt','2013-02-27 08:00:00','2013-02-28 08:00:00','BUSINESS INTELLEGENCE ','Business Intelligence and Reporting Tools (BIRT)',NULL),(7,1,'2013-02-27 19:33:49','2013-02-27 19:33:49','Product/Service Innovation<br><br><blockquote><ol><li>Create newsletter of latest trends, designs, equipment for sale, and maintenance tips on equipment</li><li>Create alliances with brokers&nbsp;</li><li>Build trust bu allowing hands on trials to contractors</li><li>Provide ongoing service support</li><li>Create relationships with brokers and dealers so they are willing to refer others to our company</li></ol></blockquote>','',NULL,NULL,'LEAD GENERATION (NORTH AMERICA)','Lead Generation for North America',NULL),(8,1,'2013-03-29 22:39:46','2013-03-29 22:39:46','','',NULL,NULL,'PROJECT-0008','Special Project',NULL),(9,68,'2013-07-13 02:41:35','2013-07-13 02:41:35','','',NULL,NULL,'Project 9','This is a created thing',NULL),(10,93,'2013-07-25 01:24:31','2013-07-25 01:24:31','','',NULL,NULL,'Project 10','project-test2013_07_24__19_23_53',NULL),(11,93,'2013-07-25 02:19:55','2013-07-25 02:19:55','','',NULL,NULL,'Project 11','project-test2013_07_24__20_19_20',NULL),(12,93,'2013-07-25 04:30:47','2013-07-25 04:30:47','','',NULL,NULL,'Project 12','project-test2013_07_24__22_30_06',NULL),(13,93,'2013-07-25 15:33:00','2013-07-25 15:33:00','','',NULL,NULL,'Project 13','project-test2013_07_25__09_32_50',NULL),(14,93,'2013-07-25 17:07:48','2013-07-25 17:07:48','','',NULL,NULL,'Project 14','project-test2013_07_25__11_07_12',NULL),(15,93,'2013-07-25 17:41:51','2013-07-25 17:41:51','','',NULL,NULL,'Project 15','project-test2013_07_25__17_41_20',NULL),(16,93,'2013-07-25 20:29:27','2013-07-25 20:29:27','','',NULL,NULL,'PROJECT-16','project-test2013_07_25__20_28_41',NULL),(17,93,'2013-07-